Package: lucy
Type: Package
Title: Really useful things done with graphs.
Version: 0.1
Author: Robert Ness
Description: Lucy is for people who think about statistics and machine learning
    problems in terms of graphs. The core data structure is the igraph object. In
    addition to handy extentions to igraph functions and visualization of igraph
    objects, Lucy implements graph algorithms that are useful across various areas
    of statistics and machine learning.
License: GPL-2
Depends:
    R (>= 2.14),
    igraph (>= 0.7.1),
    Rgraphviz,
    magrittr
Imports:
    bnlearn
Suggests:
    knitr,
    testthat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
